title: Ceiling Medallion, 1875–1906
creditline: Museum purchase from Smithsonian Institution Collections Acquisition Program and Sarah Cooper-Hewitt Funds
description:
Wallpaper roll. 
One half of a circular medallion, containing pink flowers and green foliage. Central framework is metallic gold color. Printed on off-white ground.

tombstone.epitaph:
